OL,7,FOn February 2, 2021 the man asked
OL,8,Fwhether what he was sending was too
OL,9,Fyoung, in response to which Edwards
OL,10,Ftold him not to send any underage
OL,11,Fimages, the court heard.
OL,13,FThe indecent images that were sent
OL,14,Fincluded seven category A, the worst,
OL,15,F12 category B, and 22 category C.
OL,17,FOf the category A images, the
OL,18,Festimated age of most of the children
OL,19,Fwas between 13 and 15, but one was
OL,20,Faged between seven and nine, the court
OL,21,Fwas told.
