OL,7,FSpeaking in Edwards' defence, his
OL,8,Fbarrister Philip Evans KC said:
OL,9,F"There's no suggestion in this case
OL,10,Fthat Mr Edwards has... in the
OL,11,Ftraditional sense of the word, created
OL,12,Fany image of any sort.
OL,14,F"It is important also to remember for
OL,15,Fcontext that devices, Mr Edwards'
OL,16,Fdevices, have been seized, have been
OL,17,Fsearched, and there's nothing in those
OL,18,Fdevices.
